episodes.title: S2 E27 - Jene Suplee- Holy Cult Trauma Batman
episodes.description:
S2 E27 - Jene Suplee- Holy Cult Trauma Batman- This episode deals with religious cult trauma and childhood abuse and a whole lot of laughter, healing and post-traumatic growth. Jene shares tips with Nance how to be less reactive by using her motto; Observe, Don't Absorb.








If you want us to cover a subject, or want to be a guest, or just want to see Nancy's comedy dates, reach out to Nancy Norton: /https://www.nancynorton.tv/








We found this website might be helpful to those suffering from religious trauma: https://www.recoveringfromreligion.org/#rfr-welcome
